OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnding Saturday post among 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FOfcom Royal Mail options   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Royal Mail could be allowed to scrap   
OL,6, Saturday post deliveries, as part of an
OL,7, Ofcom review into how the postal       
OL,8, service may need updating.             
OL,10,FThe regulator is set to publish a      
OL,11,Fdocument next week outlining options on
OL,12,Fhow Royal Mail can "evolve to more     
OL,13,Fclosely meet consumer needs".          
OL,15,FHowever, Ofcom - which regulates the   
OL,16,Fpostal industry - says it is not       
OL,17,Fcommenting on what the options will be.
OL,19,FRoyal Mail posted a #319m loss for the 
OL,20,Ffirst half of this financial year.     
